LANG_ENGLISH        "Yeah.  I thought you said not to fight Desann alone."
LANG_CHINESE        "是啊。我以为你说过不要单独挑战迪桑的。"

REFERENCE           15LUK015
LANG_ENGLISH        "I didn't have a choice; I never even felt him coming.  He's escaped onto a ship."
LANG_CHINESE        "我没有选择; 我甚至没有感觉到他接近。他逃到一艘船上了。"

REFERENCE           15KJO016
LANG_ENGLISH        "I know. I'm on it."
LANG_CHINESE        ""我知道。我就在那艘船上。

REFERENCE           15LUK016
LANG_ENGLISH        "We need to destroy the ship before Desann and his army reaches its target...whatever it is.  Try to find the ship's communication center, and use its sensor array to contact Rogue Squadron.  I'll keep trying..."
LANG_CHINESE        "我们必须在迪桑和他的军队到达他们的目的地之前摧毀他们....不管他们要去哪里。想办法找到那艘船的通讯中心，用那旁的侦测阵列联络侠盗中队。我会继续...."

