REFERENCE           21KJO001
LANG_ENGLISH        "Now, where would I put a communications center on a tub like this?"
LANG_CHINESE        "好了，如果是我的话，我会把通訊中心设在哪里？"

REFERENCE           21WEA001
LANG_ENGLISH        "...Leader...Katarn...Rogue Leader to Kyle Katarn..."
LANG_CHINESE        "....领队....卡塔恩....侠盗领队呼叫卡塔恩...."

REFERENCE           21KJO002
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rogue Leader, this is Kyle Katarn."
LANG_CHINESE        "侠盗领队，我是凯尔 卡塔恩。"

REFERENCE           21WEA002
LANG_ENGLISH        "Katarn, good to hear your voice.  We've locked onto your signal, and are in pursuit.  That's one whaladon of a ship you've hooked, Kyle."
LANG_CHINESE        "卡塔恩，很高兴听到你的声音。我们锁定你的讯号了，正在跟踪你们。你钓上的目标还真不是普通的大呢，凯尔。"

REFERENCE           21KJO003
LANG_ENGLISH        "Can you bring her down?"
LANG_CHINESE        "你们有办法停下这艘船吗？"

REFERENCE           21WEA003
LANG_ENGLISH        "Maybe, but I'd feel a lot better about our chances if somebody on the inside were working to disable the ship's shield array."
LANG_CHINESE        "有可能，但是如果某个船上的人负责解決掉那艘船的护盾阵列，我们的工作会轻松很多。"

REFERENCE           21KJO004
LANG_ENGLISH        "I'll see what I can about those shields, but I've got some unfinished business here."
LANG_CHINESE        "我会想办法解決那些护盾的，可是我在这里还有一些事要办。"

REFERENCE           21WEA004
LANG_ENGLISH        "Understood.  Once you get the shields down, make sure you get out of there in a hurry, because there's not going to be much left of this ship once we're done with her."
LANG_CHINESE        "了解。当你降下那艘船的护盾之后，你一定要尽快离开那里，因为我们的工作结束以后，那艘船大概不会剩下什么东西了。"

REFERENCE           21KJO005
LANG_ENGLISH        "Don't waste any time on my account."
LANG_CHINESE        "你们不用为了等我而浪费时间。"

REFERENCE           21WEA005
LANG_ENGLISH        "Good luck, Kyle.  Rogue Leader out."
LANG_CHINESE        "祝你好运，凯尔。侠盗领队通话结束。"

